Read `.claude/rules/translations.md` for the full translation rules.

Key points: `useTranslations()` for all user-visible text. Update all four locale files when adding/editing keys: `messages/en.json`, `he.json`, `es.json`, `ar.json`. Never hardcode strings in JSX.
